analysis.explanation: Pytest collection found 616 tests vs 288 in DB. Likely causes: (1) Additional test files added since DB scan, (2) Higher parametrization expansion factor than DB parser, (3) DB may filter certain test types

recommendations: Re-scan database with latest test discovery service
Verify parametrize expansion logic in backend parser
Check if DB filters out certain test types (e.g., validation tests)
Run pytest with --collect-only and update DB to match 616 count
